{
  "texts": [
    "An Andor XD Spinning Disk Confocal Microscope system with Tokai Hit incubator climate control was used for image acquisition.",
    "A Hamamatsu Flash4v2 sCMOS camera with 20×/0.75 UPlan S-APO Olympus objective was selected for higher resolution and wider view.",
    "FITC and Brightfield channels were selected for acquisition.",
    "Over 150 cells per condition were manually scored for nuclear foci using the ImageJ cell counter plug-in.",
    "BrdU incorporation assay."
  ]
}